episodes.title: Killer Grandmother | Cult Leader
episodes.description:
This video delves into the disturbing case of Tiffany Adams, a grandmother allegedly involved in a murder plot and connected to an anti-government religious group in Oklahoma known as "God's Misfits." We'll explore the details of the crime, Adams' alleged role, the custody battle that may have been a motive, and the shocking beliefs of the cult-like group she was reportedly a part of. Join us as we unpack the chilling events that led to a double homicide investigation and the arrests of Adams and her associates.

The only reason I narrated myself was even though I'm shitty at reading everyone seems to be sick of the A.I crap.
